wdi2-SH.DYN.1014.def: Probability of dying between age 10-14 years of age expressed per 1,000 adolescents age 10, if subject to age-specific mortality rates of the specified year.
wdi2-SH.DYN.1014.name: Probability of dying among adolescents ages 10-14 years
wdi2-SH.DYN.1014.source: Estimates developed by the UN Inter-agency Group for Child Mortality Estimation (UNICEF, WHO, World Bank, UN DESA Population Division) at www.childmortality.org.
